</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_189_r3l18"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / vvie ew in flugreden <expan>ankume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l19"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Techant vnd Capitel <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſant Jacob cʒü <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / v̈ber ew briefe / bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l21">in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_189_r3l20">Stat </ab></add> <expan>awſgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd leſen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd Jr doch keine ſache <expan>vved<ex>er</ex></expan> in briefen noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l22">ſüſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt die ſie <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> ew <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns begert / daʒ vvir ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l23"><expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvie es darvmb ſeÿ / Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü den Pfarrern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l24">bey vns geſchıckt / vnd das an Jn ervaren / vnd die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns cʒwen 
<del rend="strikethrough">Pr<gap reason="illegible"/></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l25">abſchrifte geweiſet / die ew antreffen / vnd die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> Schreıber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l26"><expan>abſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſen / vnd <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gebn</expan> / daʒ ſıch ewr <expan>vveiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> darnach cʒe <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l27">wiſſe / vnd vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in den vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lıeb vnd dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l28"><expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Judıca / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_189" id="93r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Erfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie ew in flugreden
                                <expan>ankume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        techant und capitel <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> sant Jacob czü
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> über ew briefe bey uns in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<add>stat</add>
<expan>awsgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und lesen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und ir doch keine sache
                            <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> in briefen noch süst
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, die sie
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> ew <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns begert, daz wir ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie es darumb sey. Also
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> czü den pfarrern bey uns geschickt und das an
                        in ervaren und die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns czwen abschrifte
                        geweiset, die ew antreffen, und die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan> schreiber
                            <expan>abschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen und
                            <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gebn</expan>, daz sich ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> darnach
                        cze <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan> wisse; und wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in den und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dienst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
